    "description": "All that remains are warring factions. Will you unite the lands as one or will you venture into its depths to find out what befell these lands?<br><br>Eldyn is a dark, medieval hack and slash MMO where you conquer territory from other players, rebels and dark evils to gain Valor, unlocking new abilities and powers along the way.<br><br>Start with a spear, rations and buckler and work your way up to unlock a vast array of varied items, equipment and abilities to give you a strategic edge against your enemies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Open world combat with up to 80 players per world<br></li><li> Free to play<br></li><li> Hack and slash combat<br></li><li> Coop play with up to 9 others<br></li><li> Boss battles<br></li><li> Command-able armies to lay siege to difficult forts<br></li><li> Wide range of items, equipment and abilities to unlock to create unique builds</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740540/extras/c350dba133d9de32e90167994c4c1430.poster.avif?t=1635787647\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740540/extras/c350dba133d9de32e90167994c4c1430.webm?t=1635787647\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740540/extras/c350dba133d9de32e90167994c4c1430.mp4?t=1635787647\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
